[The new numbers for HAV infections in this prolonged multistate outbreak are substantially lower. In part, this may be due to a significant number of states not reporting new numbers in 2+ months which may be related to diverting public health staff to COVID-19 work. In the states, however, that have kept up reporting the numbers are lower which is likely due to both the stay-at-home orders to people related to COVID-19 and the fear of ill individuals to come to healthcare facilities because of the pandemic. - Mod.LL]
